"Beauty and terror" wanders with expert views of other war zones: the Alps, the Balkans, the Eastern Front, Mesopotamia, East Africa.
On the soldiers in this book fall beehives, one celebrates Christmas under the pyramids in Egypt, tsetse flies are an insoluble problem.
